'''天主教基本戈教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Kibungensis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Kibungo}}）是[[盧旺達|盧旺達]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教基加利總教區|基加利總教區]]。

教區成立於1968年9月5日，<ref>{{cite web |title=KABGAYENSIS (KIBUNGENSIS) |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680905_kibugensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-07-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725163034/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19680905_kibugensis.html |archivedate=2019-07-25 |language=la |date=1968-09-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>位於該國[[東部省_(盧旺達)|東部省]]南部。2006年有教友412,148人（佔轄區總人口44.0%）、十二個堂區、卅五名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 19.11.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/19/181119c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725154515/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/19/181119c.html |archivedate=2019-07-25 |language=en |date=2018-11-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|費德廉·魯布埃詹加|Frédéric Rubwejanga}}和{{link-fr|基齊托·巴胡吉米希戈|Kizito Bahujimihigo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 28.08.2007 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/08/28/0439/01166.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725155948/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/08/28/0439/01166.html |archivedate=2019-07-25 |language=it |date=2007-08-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 29.01.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/01/29/0061/00141.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725162750/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/01/29/0061/00141.html |archivedate=2019-07-25 |language=it |date=2010-01-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

